
- To install prerequisites for build, installation and usage this program 
on Ubuntu/Debian do:

	sudo apt-get install g++ scons pkg-config liblua5.1-dev

- Remove stale files:

	rm -f .sconsign.dblite site_scons/*.pyc

- If you want you could configure global config file:

	gedit share/coloring_tee/config.lua
	
	or you could edit "~/.coloring_tee/config.lua" which will be made after 
	first run of program coloring_tee.

- For build and install run:

	scons
	sudo scons install
	
